### HOWTO : Mac OS X


start second skype instance             open -na /Applications/Skype.app --args -DataPath /Users/$(whoami)/Library/Application\ Support/Skype2
                                        open -na /Applications/Skype.app --args -DataPath /Users/$(whoami)/Library/Application\ Support/Skype3 etc

resize windows fluently       hold down Ctrl while resizing

# shortcuts

Umlaut                        Option + u, u/a/o
special characters window     Ctrl + Cmd + Space
open preferences              Cmd + ,
switch windows in app         Cmd + `
toggle fullscreen             Ctrl + Cmd + f
show desktop                  F11
take screenshot (full)        Cmd + Shift + 3
take screenshot (part)        Cmd + Shift + 4
show hidden files in dialog   Cmd + Shift + . (not in column view)
euro sign                     Option + Shift + 2

# firefox
home                          Option + Fn + Left
